column8: Mostly cloudy. Light winds becoming southerly 15 to 25 km/h in the early afternoon then becoming light in the late evening.

Partly cloudy. The chance of fog in the southeast suburbs in the early morning. Slight (20%) chance of a shower in the northwest suburbs, most likely in the late afternoon and evening. Near zero chance of rain elsewhere. Light winds.

Humid. Cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and evening. The chance of a thunderstorm about the nearby hills in the afternoon and evening. Light winds becoming northeast to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h during the afternoon then becoming light during the evening.

Humid early morning. Cloudy. Very high (near 100%) chance of showers, most likely in the morning and afternoon. Winds southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h turning southerly 20 to 30 km/h during the morning then increasing to 25 to 40 km/h during the day.
Cloudy. Medium (60%) chance of showers, most likely later in the day. Winds southerly 20 to 30 km/h turning southeasterly 25 to 35 km/h during the morning.
Cloudy. Slight (30%) chance of a shower. Winds southeasterly 20 to 30 km/h.
Partly cloudy. Medium (40%) chance of showers. Winds east to southeasterly 15 to 25 km/h.
